### Hadith 3:248

*Narrated Ibn 'Umar:*

Umar asked the Prophet "I vowed in the Pre-lslamic period of ignorance
to stay in Itikaf for one night in Al-Masjid al-Haram." The Prophet said
to him, "Fulfill your vow."

